sequenceDiagram
    participant C as 客户端
    participant A as 接入实例A
    participant R as Redis
    participant S as 补发扫描器
    participant M as RocketMQ

    C->>A: 秒杀请求
    A->>R: Lua预占+写待发送索引
    R-->>A: 成功
    A--xA: 发送MQ前宕机

    S->>R: 查询到期reservation
    S->>R: 获取发送租约
    S->>M: 使用原message_id补发
    M-->>S: ACK
    S->>R: 标记PUBLISHED并移出待发送索引
